  Apply patch from Dane Smith <smithdanea@gmail.com> to respect LDFLAGS. Bug
  #332791

  15 Jan 2010; Arfrever Frehtes Taifersar Arahesis <arfrever@gentoo.org>
  kudzu-1.2.83.ebuild:
  Set SUPPORT_PYTHON_ABIS. Disable installation for Python 3 (bug #300990).

  23 Aug 2009; Jeremy Olexa <darkside@gentoo.org> -files/sunlance.patch:
  remove unused patches

  31 Jan 2009; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>; metadata.xml:
  Give up maintainership; reassign to maintainer-needed.

  20 Jul 2008; Jeremy Olexa <darkside@gentoo.org> kudzu-1.2.83.ebuild:
  Make SRC_URI and explicit location. This file is hard to find on the fedora
  mirrors and hasn't been pushed to the Gentoo mirrors since its inception
  into the portage tree

  29 May 2008; Ali Polatel <hawking@gentoo.org> kudzu-1.2.71.ebuild,
